author: ajborley
msg: New interop test. Reads in XML files as SDO, converts to Axiom, sends to service. At service Axiom gets converted to SDO, SDO is compared with data from XML file (read in as SDO itself) & SDO is returned as Axiom (unless comparison failure occurs). At client returned Axiom gets converted to SDO and is compared with the original SDO.
